{"tid":1850363,"cid":31,"subCid":7,"title":"被捕手足 ：幫我重新upload「香港人」同「暴徒」兩首歌","createTime":"2020-01-29T13:17:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-21T13:17:41.000Z","uid":36155,"like":236,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":83,"replies":[{"pid":"4dabef90c5f71f359a285149b8c0088e668174d9","tid":1850363,"uid":36155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T13:17:28.000Z","msg":"相信有聽過呢2首歌既人都知原片無左<br />\n原因係有手足比狗咬後成個Channel消失左<br />\n<br />\n手足好介懷，浪費左好多人嘅心血同過百萬既點擊率<br />\n所以幫手足放番上黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Rzy79X0X4po\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRzy79X0X4po&d=m5XrLHEHhhS4xH%2BSicsBH2INpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=cf32c180\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Rzy79X0X4po</a><br />\n<br />\n暴徒 原曲 燕尾蝶<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/pobGfBTrEOY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FpobGfBTrEOY&d=m5XrLHEHhhS4xH%2BSicsBH2INpH3PnqyTY83oYMeb7B8%3D&h=b86f3cfc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/pobGfBTrEOY</a><br />\n<br />\n香港人 原曲 shall we talk"},{"pid":"f7d1c78755d81e6fd3f72efeffb711b5b3347769","tid":1850363,"uid":205482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T13:18:18.000Z","msg":"[行動]連儂/文宣十八區開花! A4 label周圍貼! 大量現成圖-即print 即貼(3)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1850261\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1850261</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e49a86e78747c57d5748fc6bbeb6bd830e4f5354","tid":1850363,"uid":36155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T13:18:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\